{"name":"Divine Allegiance","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>Starting at 7th level, when a creature within 5 feet of you takes damage, you can use your reaction to magically substitute your own health for that of the target creature, causing that creature not to take the damage. Instead, you take the damage. This damage to you can't be reduced or prevented in any way.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SCAG","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":"when a creature within 5 feet of you takes damage, you can use"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Paladin 7 (Crown)","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"adnd5e":{"itemInfo":{"type":"reaction"}},"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"SCAG","hash":"divine%20allegiance_paladin_phb_crown_scag_7_scag","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"b848b977451cd97e46857fcc1d3a99737c469b5b"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004280566,"modifiedTime":1682004280566,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"2srVvIRpVUjSL2Ur"}
{"name":"Channel Divinity: Inspiring Smite","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>Immediately after you deal damage to a creature with your Divine Smite feature, you can use your Channel Divinity as a bonus action and distribute temporary hit points to creatures of your choice within 30 feet of you, which can include you. The total number of temporary hit points equals [[/r 2d8]] + your level in this class, divided among the chosen creatures however you like.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":30,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Paladin 3 (Glory)","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/fire/projectile-wave-arrow.webp","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"TCE","hash":"channel%20divinity%3a%20inspiring%20smite_paladin_phb_glory_tce_3_tce","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"c02d30f1ecf32bdeec31b34b3d7bf5b06dc8ed38"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004280721,"modifiedTime":1682004280721,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"37DQbLOvjzDQGQ41"}
{"name":"Lay on Hands","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>Your blessed touch can heal wounds. You have a pool of healing power that replenishes when you take a long rest. With that pool, you can restore a total number of hit points equal to your paladin level × 5.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div><p>As an action, you can touch a creature and draw power from the pool to restore a number of hit points to that creature, up to the maximum amount remaining in your pool.</p><p>Alternatively, you can expend 5 hit points from your pool of healing to cure the target of one disease or neutralize one poison affecting it. You can cure multiple diseases and neutralize multiple poisons with a single use of Lay on Hands, expending hit points separately for each one.</p><p>This feature has no effect on undead and constructs.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":"Target cannot be Undead or a Construct."},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"touch"},"uses":{"value":5,"max":"5 * @classes.paladin.levels","per":"lr","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Paladin 1","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"classFeature","source":"PHB","hash":"lay%20on%20hands_paladin_phb_1_phb","propDroppable":"classFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"c9e3f8aa6d41077b8aeacfad9ab6e3a201066901"}},"img":"icons/magic/light/orbs-hand-gray.webp","_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004281381,"modifiedTime":1682004281381,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"3d5DDyUUvBMYmUMy"}
{"name":"Oathbreaker Channel Divinity: Dreadful Aspect","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>As an action, the paladin channels the darkest emotions and focuses them into a burst of magical menace. Each creature of the paladin's choice within 30 feet of the paladin must make a Wisdom saving throw if it can see the paladin. On a failed save, the target is @condition[frightened] of the paladin for 1 minute. If a creature @condition[frightened] by this effect ends its turn more than 30 feet away from the paladin, it can attempt another Wisdom saving throw to end the effect on it.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"DMG","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":30,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Paladin 3 (Oathbreaker)","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"DMG","hash":"oathbreaker%20channel%20divinity%3a%20dreadful%20aspect_paladin_phb_oathbreaker_dmg_3_dmg","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"a6a63fb5e56f00a84472e4a5e6916901dc440006"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004279845,"modifiedTime":1682004279845,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"5HKUNa1RxBukWE3G"}
{"name":"Mythic Swashbuckler","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>At 20th level, you learn to channel the spirits of historic sea captains to briefly become a paragon of heroic adventure. As an action, you embrace these spirits of the sea, gaining the following benefits for 1 minute:</p><ul class=\"rd__list\"><li class=\"rd__li \">Climbing costs no additional movement, and you have advantage on Strength (@skill[Athletics]) checks that involve climbing.</li><li class=\"rd__li \">If you are within 5 feet of a creature, and no other creatures are within 5 feet of you, you have advantage on your attacks against that creature.</li><li class=\"rd__li \">You can take the @action[Dodge] action as a bonus action.</li><li class=\"rd__li \">You have advantage on all Dexterity ability checks and Dexterity saving throws against effects that you can see.</li></ul><p>Once you use this feature, you can't use it again until you finish a long rest.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"OoOS","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Paladin 20 (Open Sea)","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"MercerOotOS","hash":"mythic%20swashbuckler_paladin_phb_open%20sea_mercerootos_20_mercerootos","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"f4fb9d381dc7476577feaba00a2837b31ddb849b"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004279698,"modifiedTime":1682004279698,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"5coRxRnAgLwEVXGZ"}
{"name":"Tenets of the Watchers","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>A paladin who assumes the Oath of the Watchers swears to safeguard mortal realms from otherworldly threats.</p><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><h3 class=\"rd__h rd__h--2\" data-title-index=\"3100\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Vigilance</span><span class=\"ve-flex-vh-center\"><span class=\"rd__h-toggle ml-2 clickable\" data-rd-h-toggle-button=\"true\">[–]</span></span></h3> <p>The threats you face are cunning, powerful, and subversive. Be ever alert for their corruption.</p></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><h3 class=\"rd__h rd__h--2\" data-title-index=\"3101\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Loyalty</span><span class=\"ve-flex-vh-center\"><span class=\"rd__h-toggle ml-2 clickable\" data-rd-h-toggle-button=\"true\">[–]</span></span></h3> <p>Never accept gifts or favors from fiends or those who truck with them. Stay true to your order, your comrades, and your duty.</p></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><h3 class=\"rd__h rd__h--2\" data-title-index=\"3102\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Discipline</span><span class=\"ve-flex-vh-center\"><span class=\"rd__h-toggle ml-2 clickable\" data-rd-h-toggle-button=\"true\">[–]</span></span></h3> <p>You are the shield against the endless terrors that lie beyond the stars. Your blade must be forever sharp and your mind keen to survive what lies beyond.</p></div></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Paladin 3 (Watchers)","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"TCE","hash":"tenets%20of%20the%20watchers_paladin_phb_watchers_tce_3_tce","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"8e7b207bfcc25b468a3cc8984b01bb435dd7ebf0"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004280912,"modifiedTime":1682004280912,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"7Tw1hy4MqqeR8cwv"}
{"name":"Channel Divinity: Turn the Tide","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>As a bonus action, you can bolster injured creatures with your Channel Divinity. Each creature of your choice that can hear you within 30 feet of you regains hit points equal to [[/r 1d6]] + your Charisma modifier (minimum of 1) if it has no more than half of its hit points.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SCAG","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":30,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"heal","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Paladin 3 (Crown)","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/fire/projectile-wave-arrow.webp","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"SCAG","hash":"channel%20divinity%3a%20turn%20the%20tide_paladin_phb_crown_scag_3_scag","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"a7a1d21472ca08f02b25bc3a1d68e88828b709c0"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004280514,"modifiedTime":1682004280514,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"7Xzbdq2F4Cjg1bDI"}
{"name":"Channel Divinity: Turn the Faithless","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>You can use your Channel Divinity to utter ancient words that are painful for fey and fiends to hear. As an action, you present your holy symbol, and each fey or fiend within 30 feet of you that can hear you must make a Wisdom saving throw. On a failed save, the creature is turned for 1 minute or until it takes damage.</p><p>A turned creature must spend its turns trying to move as far away from you as it can, and it can't willingly move to a space within 30 feet of you. It also can't take reactions. For its action, it can use only the @action[Dash] action or try to escape from an effect that prevents it from moving. If there's nowhere to move, the creature can use the @action[Dodge] action.</p><p>If the creature's true form is concealed by an illusion, shapeshifting, or other effect, that form is revealed while it is turned.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":30,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Paladin 3 (Ancients)","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/fire/projectile-wave-arrow.webp","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"PHB","hash":"channel%20divinity%3a%20turn%20the%20faithless_paladin_phb_ancients_phb_3_phb","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"c9a4a43dd3b98bd458d17edae82de21293a99dee"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemV