{"name":"Martial Versatility","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p><i>4th-level paladin @variantrule[optional class features|tce|optional feature]</i></p><p>Whenever you reach a level in this class that grants the Ability Score Improvement feature, you can replace a <a href=\"https://5etools-mirror-1.github.io/optionalfeatures.html#blankhash,flstfeature%20type:fs%3ap=1\">fighting style</a> you know with another fighting style available to paladins. This replacement represents a shift of focus in your martial practice.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Paladin 4","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"classFeature","source":"TCE","hash":"martial%20versatility_paladin_phb_4_tce","propDroppable":"classFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"3e03d6a332487001794d72d0a2fdb1a26f262b53"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004281529,"modifiedTime":1682004281529,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"I0CziIeVv5ZKnVSL"}
{"name":"Vigilant Rebuke","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p><i>15th-level Oath of the Watchers feature</i></p><p>You've learned how to chastise anyone who dares wield beguilements against you and your wards. Whenever you or a creature you can see within 30 feet of you succeeds on an Intelligence, a Wisdom, or a Charisma saving throw, you can use your reaction to deal [[/r 2d8]] + your Charisma modifier force damage to the creature that forced the saving throw.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":"Whenever you or a creature you can see within 30 feet of you succeeds on an Intelligence, a Wisdom, or a Charisma saving throw, you can use"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["2d8","force"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Paladin 15 (Watchers)","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"adnd5e":{"itemInfo":{"type":"reaction"}},"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"TCE","hash":"vigilant%20rebuke_paladin_phb_watchers_tce_15_tce","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"4e8bb41a6bdd084ebf51baeb9db77eda34a0ae0d"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004280953,"modifiedTime":1682004280953,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"I3MF8xdgqfHuAXJM"}
{"name":"Oath Spells","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>You gain oath spells at the paladin levels listed.</p><table class=\"w-100 rd__table  stripe-odd-table\"><caption>Oath of the Open Sea Spells</caption><thead><tr><th class=\"col-3 text-center\" data-rd-isroller=\"false\">Paladin Level</th><th class=\"col-9\" data-rd-isroller=\"false\">Spells</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class=\"col-3 text-center\">3rd</td><td class=\"col-9\">@spell[create or destroy water], @spell[expeditious retreat]</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-3 text-center\">5th</td><td class=\"col-9\">@spell[augury], @spell[misty step]</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-3 text-center\">9th</td><td class=\"col-9\">@spell[call lightning], @spell[tidal wave|XGE]</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-3 text-center\">13th</td><td class=\"col-9\">@spell[control water], @spell[freedom of movement]</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-3 text-center\">17th</td><td class=\"col-9\">@spell[commune with nature], @spell[maelstrom|XGE]</td></tr></tbody></table></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"OoOS","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Paladin 3 (Open Sea)","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"MercerOotOS","hash":"oath%20spells_paladin_phb_open%20sea_mercerootos_3_mercerootos","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"691157efae9d270fc639d4ef5fe58d5e20b94b