{"name":"Aura of Protection","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>Starting at 6th level, whenever you or a friendly creature within 10 feet of you must make a saving throw, the creature gains a bonus to the saving throw equal to your Charisma modifier (with a minimum bonus of +1). You must be conscious to grant this bonus.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div><p>At 18th level, the range of this aura increases to 30 feet.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":null,"type":"self"},"range":{"value":10,"long":30,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Paladin 6","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"classFeature","source":"PHB","hash":"aura%20of%20protection_paladin_phb_6_phb","propDroppable":"classFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"79634e0577c14bbbce003e73b8d6e969b6633b9f"}},"img":"icons/magic/air/wind-tornado-wall-blue.webp","_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004281563,"modifiedTime":1682004281563,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"RYqa1PXtUdYHxNyC"}
{"name":"Oathbreaker","type":"subclass","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"mb-2 ve-flex-col\"><p><i class=\"ve-muted\">Note: importing a class as an item is provided for display purposes only. If you wish to import a class to a character sheet, please use the importer on the sheet instead.</i></p><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--0\"><div data-source=\"DMG\" class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><h2 class=\"rd__h rd__h--1\" data-title-index=\"1193\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Oathbreaker</span><span class=\"ve-flex-vh-center\"> <span class=\"rd__title-link \"><span class=\"help-subtle\" title=\"Dungeon Master’s Guide\">DMG</span> p97</span><span class=\"rd__h-toggle ml-2 clickable\" data-rd-h-toggle-button=\"true\">[–]</span></span></h2> <p>An Oathbreaker is a paladin who breaks his or her sacred oaths to pursue some dark ambition or serve an evil power. Whatever light burned in the paladin's heart has been extinguished. Only darkness remains.</p><p>A paladin must be evil and at least 3rd level to become an Oathbreaker. The paladin replaces the features specific to his or her Sacred Oath with Oathbreaker features.</p><div data-source=\"DMG\" class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><h3 class=\"rd__h rd__h--2\" data-title-index=\"1194\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Oathbreaker Spells</span><span class=\"ve-flex-vh-center\"> <span class=\"rd__title-link \"><span class=\"help-subtle\" title=\"Dungeon Master’s Guide\">DMG</span> p97</span><span class=\"rd__h-toggle ml-2 clickable\" data-rd-h-toggle-button=\"true\">[–]</span></span></h3> <p>You gain oathbreaker spells at the paladin levels listed.</p><table class=\"w-100 rd__table  stripe-odd-table\"><caption>Oathbreaker Spells</caption><thead><tr><th class=\"col-2 text-center\" data-rd-isroller=\"false\">Paladin Level</th><th class=\"col-10\" data-rd-isroller=\"false\">Spells</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class=\"col-2 text-center\">3rd</td><td class=\"col-10\">@spell[hellish rebuke], @spell[inflict wounds]</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-2 text-center\">5th</td><td class=\"col-10\">@spell[crown of madness], @spell[darkness]</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-2 text-center\">9th</td><td class=\"col-10\">@spell[animate dead], @spell[bestow curse]</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-2 text-center\">13th</td><td class=\"col-10\">@spell[blight], @spell[confusion]</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-2 text-center\">17th</td><td class=\"col-10\">@spell[contagion], @spell[dominate person]</td></tr></tbody></table></div><div data-source=\"DMG\" class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><h3 class=\"rd__h rd__h--2\" data-title-index=\"1195\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Oathbreaker Channel Divinity: Control Undead</span><span class=\"ve-flex-vh-center\"> <span class=\"rd__title-link \"><span class=\"help-subtle\" title=\"Dungeon Master’s Guide\">DMG</span> p97</span><span class=\"rd__h-toggle ml-2 clickable\" data-rd-h-toggle-button=\"true\">[–]</span></span></h3> <p>As an action, the paladin targets one undead creature he or she can see within 30 feet of him or her. The target must make a Wisdom saving throw. On a failed save, the target must obey the paladin's commands for the next 24 hours, or until the paladin uses this Channel Divinity option again. An undead whose challenge rating is equal to or greater than the paladin's level is immune to this effect.</p></div><div data-source=\"DMG\" class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><h3 class=\"rd__h rd__h--2\" data-title-index=\"1196\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Oathbreaker Channel Divinity: Dreadful Aspect</span><span class=\"ve-flex-vh-center\"> <span class=\"rd__title-link \"><span class=\"help-subtle\" title=\"Dungeon Master’s Guide\">DMG</span> p97</span><span class=\"rd__h-toggle ml-2 clickable\" data-rd-h-toggle-button=\"true\">[–]</span></span></h3> <p>As an action, the paladin channels the darkest emotions and focuses them into a burst of magical menace. Each creature of the paladin's choice within 30 feet of the paladin must make a Wisdom saving throw if it can see the paladin. On a failed save, the target is @condition[frightened] of the paladin for 1 minute. If a creature @condition[frightened] by this effect ends its turn more than 30 feet away from the paladin, it can attempt another Wisdom saving throw to end the effect on it.</p></div></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><div data-source=\"DMG\" class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><h3 class=\"rd__h rd__h--2\" data-title-index=\"1197\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Aura of Hate</span><span class=\"ve-flex-vh-center\"> <span class=\"rd__title-link \"><span class=\"help-subtle\" title=\"Dungeon Master’s Guide\">DMG</span> p97</span><span class=\"rd__h-toggle ml-2 clickable\" data-rd-h-toggle-button=\"true\">[–]</span></span></h3> <p>Starting at 7th level, the paladin, as well any fiends and undead within 10 feet of the paladin, gains a bonus to melee weapon damage rolls equal to the paladin's Charisma modifier (minimum of +1). A creature can benefit from this feature from only one paladin at a time.</p><p>At 18th level, the range of this aura increases to 30 feet.</p></div></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><div data-source=\"DMG\" class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><h3 class=\"rd__h rd__h--2\" data-title-index=\"1198\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Supernatural Resistance</span><span class=\"ve-flex-vh-center\"> <span class=\"rd__title-link \"><span class=\"help-subtle\" title=\"Dungeon Master’s Guide\">DMG</span> p97</span><span class=\"rd__h-toggle ml-2 clickable\" data-rd-h-toggle-button=\"true\">[–]</span></span></h3> <p>At 15th level, the paladin gains resistance to bludgeoning, piercing, and slashing damage from nonmagical weapons.</p></div></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><div data-source=\"DMG\" class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><h3 class=\"rd__h rd__h--2\" data-title-index=\"1199\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Dread Lord</span><span class=\"ve-flex-vh-center\"> <span class=\"rd__title-link \"><span class=\"help-subtle\" title=\"Dungeon Master’s Guide\">DMG</span> p97</span><span class=\"rd__h-toggle ml-2 clickable\" data-rd-h-toggle-button=\"true\">[–]</span></span></h3> <p>At 20th level, the paladin can, as an action, surround himself or herself with an aura of gloom that lasts for 1 minute. The aura reduces any bright light in a 30-foot radius around the paladin to dim light. Whenever an enemy that is @condition[frightened] by the paladin starts its turn in the aura, it takes [[/r 4d10]] psychic damage. Additionally, the paladin and creatures he or she chooses in the aura are draped in deeper shadow. Creatures that rely on sight have disadvantage on attack rolls against creatures draped in this shadow.</p><p>While the aura lasts, the paladin can use a bonus action on his or her turn to cause the shadows in the aura to attack one creature. The paladin makes a melee spell attack against the target. If the attack hits, the target takes necrotic damage equal to [[/r 3d10]] + the paladin's Charisma modifier.</p><p>After activating the aura, the paladin can't do so again until he or she finishes a long rest.</p></div></div></div></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"DMG","identifier":"oathbreaker","classIdentifier":"paladin","advancement":[],"spellcasting":{"progression":"none","ability":""}},"flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"classes.html","source":"PHB","hash":"paladin_phb","sourceSubclass":"DMG","hashSubclass":"paladin_phb,state:sub-oathbreaker-dmg=b1","propDroppable":"subclass","filterValues":{"Source":{"TCE":1,"ERLW":1,"UA2020SubclassesPt3":0,"UAArtificerRevisited":1,"UAClassFeatureVariants":0,"UAArtificer":0,"PHB":1,"XGE":1,"UABarbarianPrimalPaths":0,"UARevisedSubclasses":0,"SCAG":1,"UA2020SubclassesPt1":0,"UABarbarianAndMonk":0,"UA2020SubclassesPt2":0,"UABardAndPaladin":0,"UABardBardColleges":0,"UAKitsOfOld":0,"VRGR":1,"UA2020SubclassesPt4":0,"UATheRangerRevised":0,"UA2021MagesOfStrixhaven":0,"PSA":1,"UAModernMagic":0,"DMG":1,"UAClericDivineDomains":0,"GGR":1,"UAOrderDomain":0,"UAClericDruidWizard":0,"UADruid":0,"UAThreeSubclasses"