{"name":"Oathbreaker Channel Divinity: Control Undead","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>As an action, the paladin targets one undead creature he or she can see within 30 feet of him or her. The target must make a Wisdom saving throw. On a failed save, the target must obey the paladin's commands for the next 24 hours, or until the paladin uses this Channel Divinity option again. An undead whose challenge rating is equal to or greater than the paladin's level is immune to this effect.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"DMG","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":24,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":30,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Paladin 3 (Oathbreaker)","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"DMG","hash":"oathbreaker%20channel%20divinity%3a%20control%20undead_paladin_phb_oathbreaker_dmg_3_dmg","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"6cd0cfed8c0b546d4ba4a1944c4bf4af9c3bae88"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004279824,"modifiedTime":1682004279824,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"d6x9bJbRhzsR1348"}
{"name":"Mortal Bulwark","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p><i>20th-level Oath of the Watchers feature</i></p><p>You manifest a spark of divine power in defense of the mortal realms. As a bonus action, you gain the following benefits for 1 minute:</p><ul class=\"rd__list\"><li class=\"rd__li \">You gain @sense[truesight] with a range of 120 feet.</li><li class=\"rd__li \">You have advantage on attack rolls against aberrations, celestials, elementals, fey, and fiends.</li><li class=\"rd__li \">When you hit a creature with an attack roll and deal damage to it, you can also force it to make a Charisma saving throw against your spell save DC. On a failed save, the creature is magically banished to its native plane of existence if it's currently not there. On a successful save, the creature can't be banished by this feature for 24 hours.</li></ul><p>Once you use this bonus action, you can't use it again until you finish a long rest, unless you expend a 5th-level spell slot to use it again.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"cha","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Paladin 20 (Watchers)","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"TCE","hash":"mortal%20bulwark_paladin_phb_watchers_tce_20_tce","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"aaf005f6961f5293bb8406e3d88ab2f8c899bc62"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004280966,"modifiedTime":1682004280966,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"dgnXyQtrD3drAjGi"}
{"name":"Purity of Spirit","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>Beginning at 15th level, you are always under the effects of a @spell[protection from evil and good] spell.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":"","long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Oath of Devotion 15","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"PHB","hash":"purity%20of%20spirit_paladin_phb_devotion_phb_15_phb","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"5f2f93c2854064ee6dafb03a94dc335d075c9ba7"}},"img":"icons/skills/toxins/poison-bottle-corked-fire-green.webp","_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004280283,"modifiedTime":1682004280283,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"duPo3nTS8C6MCPTS"}
{"name":"Tenets of Devotion","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>Though the exact words and strictures of the Oath of Devotion vary, paladins of this oath share these tenets.</p><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"3046\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Honesty.</span></span> <p>Don't lie or cheat. Let your word be your promise.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"3047\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Courage.</span></span> <p>Never fear to act, though caution is wise.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"3048\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Compassion.</span></span> <p>Aid others, protect the weak, and punish those who threaten them. Show mercy to your foes, but temper it with wisdom.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"3049\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Honor.</span></span> <p>Treat others with fairness, and let your honorable deeds be an example to them. Do as much good as possible while causing the least amount of harm.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"3050\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Duty.</span></span> <p>Be responsible for your actions and their consequences, protect those entrusted to your care, and obey those who have just authority over you.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div></div></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Paladin 3 (Devotion)","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"PHB","hash":"tenets%20of%20devotion_paladin_phb_devotion_phb_3_phb","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"e6515427c87ac381ae430e9d0c60ae2df073a9bf"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004280236,"modifiedTime":1682004280236,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"fTxL0tUUy9mVUM04"}
{"name":"Aura of Warding","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>Beginning at 7th level, ancient magic lies so heavily upon you that it forms an eldritch ward. You and friendly creatures within 10 feet of you have resistance to damage from spells.</p><p>At 18th level, the range of this aura increases to 30 feet.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Paladin 7 (Ancients)","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"PHB","hash":"aura%20of%20warding_paladin_phb_ancients_phb_7_phb","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"8b0f2522e71a09ffc45c317b4e94e66948ac36df"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004280039,"modifiedTime":1682004280039,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"feRE3fJsAQmN0lM6"}
{"name":"Divine Smite","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>Starting at 2nd level, when you hit a creature with a melee weapon attack, you can expend one spell slot to deal radiant damage to the target, in addition to the weapon's damage. The extra damage is [[/r 2d8]] for a 1st-level spell slot, plus [[/r 1d8]] for each spell level higher than 1st, to a maximum of [[/r 5d8]]. The damage increases by [[/r 1d8]] if the target is an undead or a fiend, to a maximum of [[/r 6d8]].</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB","activation":{"type":"special","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["2d8","radiant"]],"versatile":"1d8"},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Paladin 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"classFeature","source":"PHB","hash":"divine%20smite_paladin_phb_2_phb","propDroppable":"classFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"4a64b337602f2d76305feba9fc748c2e4fc3a42c"}},"img":"icons/skills/melee/weapons-crossed-swords-yellow-teal.webp","_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004281400,"modifiedTime":1682004281400,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"gW7xu7hnQqkiHhMx"}
{"name":"Supernova","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>At 20th level, you gain the ability become the realization of the end of a star's life. As an action, you can magically infuse yourself with starlight, gaining the following benefits for 1 minutes:</p><ul class=\"rd__list\"><li class=\"rd__li \">You emit bright light in a 60-foot radius and dim light for an additional 60 feet.</li><li class=\"rd__li \">Your weapon attacks deal an additional [[/r 3d8]] radiant damage on a hit.</li><li class=\"rd__li \">When you use your Divine Smite feature, double the number of dice rolled for the radiant damage.</li></ul><p>Once you use this feature, you can't use it again until you finish a long rest.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ATLAS","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["3d8","radiant"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Paladin 20 (North Star (ATLAS))","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"ATLAS","hash":"supernova_paladin_phb_north%20star%20(atlas)_atlas_20_atlas","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"c6d3a5b617768a726a1e989309b9b00082d1e282"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004279778,"modifiedTime":1682004279778,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"h05bYv8CM