{"name":"Channel Divinity: Guided Strike","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>You can use your Channel Divinity to strike with supernatural accuracy. When you make an attack roll, you can use your Channel Divinity to gain a +10 bonus to the roll. You make this choice after you see the roll, but before the DM says whether the attack hits or misses.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Paladin 3 (Conquest)","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"icons/magic/fire/projectile-wave-arrow.webp","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"XGE","hash":"channel%20divinity%3a%20guided%20strike_paladin_phb_conquest_xge_3_xge","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"7c2cf9c50d7e880f32ec351f35f2079dea9f8f52"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004281029,"modifiedTime":1682004281029,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"pmy29cAmy6TNsjoa"}
{"name":"Scornful Rebuke","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>Starting at 15th level, those who dare to strike you are psychically punished for their audacity. Whenever a creature hits you with an attack, that creature takes psychic damage equal to your Charisma modifier (minimum of 1) if you're not @condition[incapacitated].</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Paladin 15 (Conquest)","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"XGE","hash":"scornful%20rebuke_paladin_phb_conquest_xge_15_xge","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"cd0fc0f408d2f25084138e524093dba623a573b9"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004281098,"modifiedTime":1682004281098,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"pvU8CM93bPN3Bu5U"}
{"name":"Tenets of Glory","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>The tenets of the Oath of Glory drive a paladin to attempt heroics that might one day shine in legend.</p><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><h3 class=\"rd__h rd__h--2\" data-title-index=\"3086\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Actions over Words</span><span class=\"ve-flex-vh-center\"><span class=\"rd__h-toggle ml-2 clickable\" data-rd-h-toggle-button=\"true\">[–]</span></span></h3> <p>Strive to be known by glorious deeds, not words.</p></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><h3 class=\"rd__h rd__h--2\" data-title-index=\"3087\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Challenges Are but Tests</span><span class=\"ve-flex-vh-center\"><span class=\"rd__h-toggle ml-2 clickable\" data-rd-h-toggle-button=\"true\">[–]</span></span></h3> <p>Face hardships with courage, and encourage your allies to face them with you.</p></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><h3 class=\"rd__h rd__h--2\" data-title-index=\"3088\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Hone the Body</span><span class=\"ve-flex-vh-center\"><span class=\"rd__h-toggle ml-2 clickable\" data-rd-h-toggle-button=\"true\">[–]</span></span></h3> <p>Like raw stone, your body must be worked so its potential can be realized.</p></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><h3 class=\"rd__h rd__h--2\" data-title-index=\"3089\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Discipline the Soul</span><span class=\"ve-flex-vh-center\"><span class=\"rd__h-toggle ml-2 clickable\" data-rd-h-toggle-button=\"true\">[–]</span></span></h3> <p>You must marshal the discipline to overcome failings within yourself that threaten to dim the glory of you and your friends.</p></div></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Paladin 3 (Glory)","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"TCE","hash":"tenets%20of%20glory_paladin_phb_glory_tce_3_tce","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"f2f0e1d35aee879da54a55222254fce1939c38d0"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004280699,"modifiedTime":1682004280699,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"qqGppBguY6JCciiy"}
{"name":"Oath Spells","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>You gain oath spells at the paladin levels listed.</p><table class=\"w-100 rd__table  stripe-odd-table\"><caption>Oath of Conquest Spells</caption><thead><tr><th class=\"col-2 text-center\" data-rd-isroller=\"false\">Paladin Level</th><th class=\"col-10\" data-rd-isroller=\"false\">Spells</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class=\"col-2 text-center\">3rd</td><td class=\"col-10\">@spell[armor of Agathys], @spell[command]</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-2 text-center\">5th</td><td class=\"col-10\">@spell[hold person], @spell[spiritual weapon]</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-2 text-center\">9th</td><td class=\"col-10\">@spell[bestow curse], @spell[fear]</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-2 text-center\">13th</td><td class=\"col-10\">@spell[dominate beast], @spell[stoneskin]</td></tr><tr><td class=\"col-2 text-center\">17th</td><td class=\"col-10\">@spell[cloudkill], @spell[dominate person]</td></tr></tbody></table></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Paladin 3 (Conquest)","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"XGE","hash":"oath%20spells_paladin_phb_conquest_xge_3_xge","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"23c0f91fa594057d31b7f4709de4561caa5470e0"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion